Welcome to Smith & Smith Orthodontics in Sanford, NC


Your smile is our focus
Achieving a healthy, beautiful smile can be a life-changing event, for anyone from adolescents to adults! Here at the Sanford, NC orthodontic office of Smith & Smith Orthodontics, we’ve built our practice on the idea that everyone deserves the satisfaction and confidence that comes with an amazing smile. Dr. Brian Smith and Dr. Lynn Smith specialize in individualized orthodontic care, and we take the time to understand each patient’s specific needs and goals in order to create the most beautiful smile possible.
We take pride in using high-quality, American-made products, including American Orthodontics’ Empower® self-ligating metal and clear brackets. We also offer Invisalign® clear aligner orthodontics and surgical orthodontics for children, adolescents, and adults.
When you become a patient of Smith & Smith Orthodontics, you truly become a member of our family. We look forward to meeting you and helping you achieve all your orthodontic goals. Please feel free to contact our Sanford orthodontic office, or call us at (919) 774-4744 and schedule your complimentary consultation today!











Creating
			Beautiful
			Smiles
We take the time to get to know our patients so that we can provide the best, most appropriate treatment possible. We do not have a “one size fits all” approach to orthodontics; each patient and each situation is unique and special and deserves to be treated as such. Drs. Brian and Lynn Smith love orthodontics because it's not just about teeth; it's also about building relationships




Brian D. Smith, DDS, MS



Lynn H. Smith, DDS, MS





























